rComments: The class was very challenging, but if you go to class and do all the assignments and dgd exercises it definitely helps. If you do all the assignments the lowest mark is dropped and you can replace your midterm mark with your final exam mark if it's higher.

She's confusing but then again, she teaches the hardest 1st year course offered at UofO so it's hard to judge if it's entirely her fault.  Assignments are way harder than the theory seen in class. You will be working 10-20 hours a week on them.  exams, midterms, and tests are very fair. You can easily pass if you memorize all definitions
